  "body": "#### System information\r\nerigon version 2021.10.2-alpha\r\ngit_branch=stable git_tag=v2021.10.02 git_commit=8b4d31f6617a051285e62ef065d4a9de2a439fb2\r\nOS & Version: Alpine Linux / Docker / Based on official example file\r\nNetwork: mainnet\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nrpcdaemon can successfully connect to erigon for all neccessary methods. Everything was working just fine (~2 months old version) until we upgraded to recent erigon version to support Arrow Glacier fork. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nNow after upgrade to recent version all the \"remote\" methods like `txpool_content` or `eth_sendRawTransaction` fail with same error while erigon shows no errors:\r\n```\r\ncurl -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\", \"method\": \"txpool_content\", \"params\": [], \"id\":1}' IP:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 127.0.0.1:9090: connect: connection refused\\\"\"}}\r\n```\r\nor same error from rpcdaemon docker logs for `eth_sendRawTransaction`:\r\n```\r\nrpcdaemon  | [WARN] [12-10|11:53:01.056] Served. conn=IP:59362 method=eth_sendRawTransaction reqid=0 t=200.056Âµs err=\"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 127.0.0.1:9090: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nRegular methods like `eth_blockNumber` work just fine.\r\n\r\nAre there any new steps necessary to make it work, some kind of new permission control, because we are running in remote mode based on original docker-compose setup.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n```yml\r\nservices:\r\n  erigon:\r\n    image: thorax/erigon:devel\r\n    container_name: erigon\r\n    restart: unless-stopped\r\n    volumes:\r\n      - erigon:/home/erigon/.local/share/erigon\r\n    ports:\r\n      - \"30303:30303/tcp\"\r\n      - \"30303:30303/udp\"\r\n      - \"30304:30304/tcp\"\r\n      - \"30304:30304/udp\"\r\n    command: erigon --private.api.addr=0.0.0.0:9090\r\n    networks:\r\n      - project\r\n    ....\r\n\r\n  rpcdaemon:\r\n    image: thorax/erigon:devel\r\n    command: rpcdaemon --private.api.addr=erigon:9090 --http.addr=0.0.0.0 --http.vhosts=* --http.corsdomain=* --http.api=eth,net,web3,debug,txpool,trace\r\n    container_name: rpcdaemon\r\n    ports:\r\n      - \"8545:8545\"\r\n    restart: unless-stopped\r\n    links:\r\n      - erigon\r\n    networks:\r\n      - project\r\n    ....\r\n```\r\n",
